9
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I 'll get it taken care of.</font>

10
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Noe! Call Iz-san for me.</font>

