<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there's a doctor 
who'll come to see them.</font>

34
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In unexpected situations like this,</font>

35
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or times when we go too far, yeah.</font>

36
