<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

45
00:03:08,690 --> 00:03:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

46
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you leaving already?</font>

47
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

48
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gonna visit Hela and the rest.</font>

49
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your help!</font>

50
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please...</font>

51
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please save him.</font>

52
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need immediate treatment, too!</font>

53
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

54
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault.</font>

55
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find a way to help him. Please!</font>

56
00:03:59,230 --> 00:04:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says he wants to talk.</font>

57
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wounds... are pretty bad, huh?</font>

58
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm... sorry.</font>

59
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are <i>you</i> apologizing?</font>

60
00:04:20,650 --> 00:04:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault you're...</font>

61
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu...</font>

62
00:04:31,850 --> 00:04:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one... who got 
you into this... right?</font>

63
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just... did what 
I wanted to... that's all.</font>

64
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be... just fine.</font>

65
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san...</font>

66
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

67
00:05:08,910 --> 00:05:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault someone so important 
to you is in that condition.</font>

68
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

69
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How have you been lately?</font>

70
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same as always.</font>

71
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurts every once in a while.</font>

72
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll give you the usual medicine.</font>

73
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

74
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Siu?</font>

75
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He got away.</font>

76
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dear, dear. What a problem child.</font>

77
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Running from Iz-san again?</font>

78
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not running.</font>

79
00:05:58,730 --> 00:06:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That scar...</font>

80
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always hide it, huh?</font>

81
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you haven't shown Mike or Hugh.</font>

82
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some people would worry 
about me if they saw it.</font>

83
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiding it is easier.</font>

84
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leu and Nero kept putting bandages on it.</font>

85
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, how adorable.</font>

86
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there are people who 
would be hurt by this scar.</font>

87
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

88
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it won't hurt me, so please show me.</font>

89
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How twisted are you?</font>

90
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say it looks pretty cool.</font>

91
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, without that,</font>

92
00:06:32,370 --> 00:06:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you and the others 
wouldn't be who you are now.</font>

93
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure there are things only the 
people who were there understand,</font>

94
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I can see that those scars have left 
you two with more than just regrets.</font>

95
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place is the proof of that, right?</font>

96
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cut my finger!</font>

97
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. That's a pretty big cut.</font>

98
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurts!</font>

99
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There. All done.</font>

100
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

101
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also...</font>

102
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My target frothed at the
mouth and collapsed.</font>

103
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've said that first!</font>

104
00:07:17,490 --> 00:07:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? Again?</font>

105
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to call you so frequently.</font>

106
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:23,670
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#353037">Safety First</font></b></font>

107
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:23,670
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#97363f">Let's stay safe today!</font></b></font>

108
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm such a klutz.</font>

109
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me!</font>

110
00:07:32,210 --> 00:07:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!</font>

111
00:07:34,910 --> 00:07:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a grown-up, 
aren't you? Deal with it!</font>

112
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This bear's mean!</font>

113
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not just some bear. I'm Amumu-sama!</font>

114
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiya! I see treatment is underway.</font>

115
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san, who is this?</font>

116
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, she's a nurse who works with Iz-san.</font>

117
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name is Merim.</font>

118
