127
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Thank you.</font>

128
00:08:07,130 --> 00:08:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while since the 
last time you came, Merim.</font>

129
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We came because you guys are a mess.</font>

130
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about that.</font>

131
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Iz-san said to go help 
him when you're done here.</font>

132
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You numbskull!</font>

133
00:08:21,490 --> 00:08:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've said that sooner!</font>

134
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:29,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a strange one.</font>

135
00:08:29,770 --> 00:08:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's got skills, though.</font>

136
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? She left it behind!</font>

137
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Don't worry.</font>

138
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She only uses Amumu with us.</font>

139
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Izua.</font>

140
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get the usual ready.</font>

141
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

142
00:08:48,470 --> 00:08:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your first time 
meeting Mike-kun, right?</font>

143
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get along all right?</font>

144
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much conversation was had...</font>

145
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with Amumu.</font>

146
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:56,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

147
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not speak with him normally?</font>

148
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to. I'm terrible at talking.</font>

149
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But through Amumu, I can hold 
a conversation properly.</font>

150
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Properly, huh?</font>

151
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Don't cry, kid! Look at the 
magnificence that is me!</font>

152
00:09:08,770 --> 00:09:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And children find him to be 
tremendously reassuring.</font>

153
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's that? It's so cute!</font>

154
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true enough. 
And it's a big help...</font>

155
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but speaking to others 
besides me would—</font>

156
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's fine.</font>

157
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:22,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're special, Izua.</font>

158
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doctor!</font>

159
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will my legs never get better?</font>

160
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:33,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. They'll get better.</font>

161
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be able to go wherever 
you want with this guy again.</font>

162
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amumu! But he was all torn up!</font>

163
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, your doctor happens 
to be a very amazing doctor.</font>

164
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can even fix dolls.</font>

165
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amumu's face didn't look like this before.</font>

166
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doctor, you're awful at this.</font>

167
00:09:55,530 --> 00:09:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You think so?</font>

168
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I grow up, I'll come 
and help you, Doctor.</font>

169
00:10:03,330 --> 00:10:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that would be a big help.</font>

170
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, you'll have 
to work hard to get better.</font>

171
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will!</font>

172
00:10:14,930 --> 00:10:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're done over here, too.</font>

173
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

174
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's rough when they're 
all so unhealthy, huh?</font>

