00:10:21,850 --> 00:10:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see you.</font>

176
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for all your hard work!</font>

177
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, kid!</font>

178
00:10:32,710 --> 00:10:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't interfere with Merim-chan and 
Izua's lovey-dovey time too much, okay?</font>

179
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later!</font>

180
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

181
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

182
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iz-san doesn't see her 
that way at all, though.</font>

183
00:10:45,650 --> 00:10:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

184
00:10:50,410 --> 00:10:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Izua!</font>

185
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've finished... cleaning up...</font>

186
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's sleeping in an odd place again.</font>

187
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going home.</font>

188
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

189
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:20,990
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#fefefe">The <font color="#52d234">D<font color="#fefefe">aily <font color="#f2a42a">L<font color="#fefefe">ife of a <font color="#2a62dc">P<font color="#fefefe">art-Time <font color="#c9003f">T<font color="#fefefe">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

