<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#0b0a0c">The <font color="#ad6f4d">D<font color="#0b0a0c">aily <font color="#cb0742">L<font color="#0b0a0c">ife of a <font color="#9818ec">P<font color="#0b0a0c">art-Time <font color="#eee342">T<font color="#0b0a0c">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

191
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hi there! I'm devoted 
part-time torturer Mike!</i></font>

192
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The truth is, there's another side to me.</i></font>

193
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm also a novelist who uses torturers 
as subjects for the novels I write.</i></font>

