00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,510
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#19161b">Actually 
Writes
 With a
 Keyboard</font></font></b></font>

195
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,510
