<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc"><font size="15">Torture Bullet</font></font></b></font></font>

197
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:43,470
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc"><font size="15">Torture Bullet</font></font></b></font></font>

198
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The source work has sold even better 
since it got a manga adaptation!</font>

199
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're having to do 
yet another huge reprint!</font>

200
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that novel of mine seems 
to be a hit at the moment.</i></font>

201
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just doesn't feel real.</font>

202
00:11:50,430 --> 00:11:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, make it feel real, please!</font>

203
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:57,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've always written 
psychological suspense novels,</i></font>

204
00:11:57,110 --> 00:12:00,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but when I made torture the theme 
and shone a spotlight on the characters,</i></font>

205
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it was much better received 
than I expected.</i></font>

206
00:12:03,130 --> 00:12:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your readership has started to stabilize,</font>

207
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so should we do a longer work?</font>

208
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds good!</font>

209
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go ask for some more stories 
and think up some ideas.</font>

210
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stories?</font>

211
00:12:14,510 --> 00:12:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, from the people at your part-time 
job that you used as inspiration?</font>

212
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. The legendary torturers 
who are my mentors.</font>

213
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked you this before...</font>

214
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but do these torturers really exist?</font>

215
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said...</font>

216
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they do exist!</font>

217
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then would you like me to tell 
you about my mentors again?</font>

218
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

219
00:12:41,610 --> 00:12:44,320
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

220
00:12:41,610 --> 00:12:44,320
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

221
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of my mentors is Se—um, A-san.</font>

222
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Sup?</font>

223
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-san is Spirytus's ace.</font>

224
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would it be all right if 
I observed your next job?</font>

225
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. No problem.</font>

226
00:12:55,890 --> 00:12:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does a human have twenty nails?</font>

227
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I finally know the answer.</font>

228
00:13:01,170 --> 00:13:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's for people like you...</font>

229
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who just don't know when to give up!</font>

230
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike, are you heading home?</font>

231
00:13:12,070 --> 00:13:14,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I'm all done!</font>

232
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's grab dinner together.</font>

233
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Thanks for treating me!</font>

234
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really want to try doing that.</font>

235
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That, huh? It's hard 
to get it just right.</font>

236
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we give it 
a try together next time?</font>

237
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

238
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's like a big brother who's really 
good at looking after people.</font>

239
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:40,420
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

240
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:40,420
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

241
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My second mentor is Si—er, B-san.</font>

242
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

243
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's like the on-site boss.</font>

244
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's solved all kinds of big cases,</font>

245
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he's famous in the torture industry.</font>

246
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can be a little scary...</font>

247
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What was that mistake? 
How many years have you been doing this?</font>

248
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

249
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he's really nice to us rookies.</font>

250
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You did well on that job yesterday.</font>

251
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thank you!</font>

252
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:01,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I worry that you give your daughters 
that same kind of education.</font>

253
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid? Of course I don't.</font>

254
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's Papa to two adorable daughters!</font>

255
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:10,740
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

256
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:10,740
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fbfafc">Torture Bullet</font></b></font></font>

257
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's what the two 
I used as inspiration are like.</font>

258
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Are you certain 
you didn't make them up?</font>

259
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, they really exist!</font>

260
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike.</font>

261
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear your novels have been 
doing really well lately.</font>

262
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to you.</font>

263
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm going to be writing 
a slightly heavier story this time,</font>

264
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'd love to hear some more 
stories from both of you...</font>

265
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem.</font>

266
00:14:35,190 --> 00:14:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heavier, huh?</font>

267
00:14:40,770 --> 00:14:43,690
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an4}</font><b><font size="25"><font color="#1a171c">Currently being told about major</font></font></b>

268
00:14:41,810 --> 00:14:44,900
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an4}</font><b><font size="25"><font color="#1a171c">cases that everyone would recognize.</font></font></b>

269
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like that?</font>

270
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think those cases are 
a little too well-known.</font>

271
00:14:52,050 --> 00:14:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to do research,</font>

272
00:14:53,530 --> 00:14:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should look through 
the documents Noe has.</font>

273
00:14:56,230 --> 00:14:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go try that!</font>

274
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

275
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, it's a little late to ask,</font>

276
00:15:02,170 --> 00:15:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but do you hate the 
characters I modeled after you?</font>

277
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I am exaggerating 
them a lot when I write them.</font>

278
00:15:08,460 --> 00:15:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean like, 
"the Legendary Torturer"?</font>

279
00:15:09,010 --> 00:15:16,890
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#09070b">Legendary
 Torturer</font></font></b></font>

280
00:15:11,540 --> 00:15:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And his apprentice being 
"the Genius Torturer."</font>

281
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:16,890
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#09070b">Genius
Torturer</font></font></b></font>

282
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really think anything of it.</font>

283
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pretty much the truth anyway.</font>

284
00:15:18,890 --> 00:15:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

285
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:20,690
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#1f1922">Right?</font></b></font></font>

286
00:15:19,930 --> 00:15:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty much.</font>

287
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:21,810
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#1f1922">Pretty
 much.</font></b></font></font>

288
00:15:21,190 --> 00:15:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's so them.</i></font>

289
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's the kind of case you want...</font>

290
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The files around here should do.</font>

291
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is such a huge help!</font>

292
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your novel seems to be quite a hot topic.</font>

293
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm grateful that so many 
people are reading it.</font>

294
00:15:36,950 --> 00:15:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The torture industry has 
a very negative image,</font>

295
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but maybe your readers will gain 
a better understanding of it.</font>

296
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:47,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san was happy about it, too.</font>

297
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep working hard for us, okay?</font>

298
00:15:48,650 --> 00:15:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will!</font>

299
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're not comfortable 
torturing people, right?</font>

300
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you all right reading my novel?</font>

301
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was fine on that front.</font>

302
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I reduced my imagination to the 
bare minimum and treated it as data.</font>

303
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:06,650
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#1c151f"><font size="16">I do the same for
 the reports.</font></font></b></font></font>

304
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

305
00:16:08,950 --> 00:16:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoo-hoo! Las-kun!</font>

306
00:16:13,110 --> 00:16:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

307
00:16:13,610 --> 00:16:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-san! Hugh!</font>

308
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you come to listen 
to the professor again?</font>

309
00:16:18,570 --> 00:16:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

310
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he wanted to ask about some 
torture methods touched on in the novel.</font>

311
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Torture Bullet</i> is pretty popular, huh?</font>

312
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:29,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you put me somewhere 
in your novels, too?</font>

313
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

314
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?</font>

315
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to be a character
 who can or can't keep a secret?</font>

316
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I'll be a character 
who gets tortured, huh?</font>

317
00:16:38,930 --> 00:16:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One who can keep a secret, then.</font>

318
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

319
00:16:46,580 --> 00:16:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was helpful in so many ways.</font>

320
00:16:49,660 --> 00:16:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-san, why did you 
decide to write novels?</font>

321
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe... because it seemed interesting?</font>

322
00:16:56,710 --> 00:16:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are things that 
aren't possible in real life,</font>

323
00:16:58,730 --> 00:17:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or that are possible, 
but you can't do them,</font>

324
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and things that you don't 
want to do at all, right?</font>

325
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fiction doesn't have 
those kinds of limitations.</font>

326
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Diving into stuff that's different 
from everyday life is fun.</font>

327
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why you dove into something 
that's different from the norm?</font>

328
00:17:14,590 --> 00:17:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what this part-time 
torturing job is, right?</font>

329
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's true.</font>

330
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You started torturing because you 
were looking for material, right?</font>

331
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you feel totally at home in it.</font>

332
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a funny thing, isn't it?</font>

333
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is.</font>

334
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The world that I thought was so different 
from the norm has become my daily life.</font>

335
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If not for my writing, 
I'd never have jumped in.</font>

336
00:17:38,140 --> 00:17:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if writing was all I did, 
I'd never have found it.</font>

337
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad I tried both.</font>

338
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plot you sent me 
was absolutely wonderful!</font>

339
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just when you think it'll be all 
about the main characters,</font>

340
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in comes a new character!</font>

341
00:17:55,450 --> 00:17:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone who gains something precious 
through finding work as a torturer.</font>

342
00:17:59,570 --> 00:18:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a classic sort of theme, 
but it's lovely!</font>

343
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

344
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It felt like you were even more 
passionate about this than usual.</font>

345
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this new character modeled 
after someone, too?</font>

346
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a secret.</font>

347
00:18:18,850 --> 00:18:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cleaning, cleaning! La, la, la, la, la!</font>

348
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

349
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've discovered a mysterious box!</font>

350
00:18:28,780 --> 00:18:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want it!</font>

351
00:18:30,470 --> 00:18:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

352
00:18:39,890 --> 00:18:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is...</font>

353
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! These bring back memories!</font>

354
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are the games we 
used to play to kill time!</font>

355
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the two of you play games like these?</font>

356
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We played them quite a bit.</font>

357
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To figure out stuff like who 
would torture the annoying target.</font>

358
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd use these to decide.</font>

359
00:18:59,710 --> 00:19:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

360
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

361
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">here we have one page of instructions.</font>

362
00:19:06,430 --> 00:19:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The target is an ideological offender.</font>

363
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An ideological offender?</i></font>

364
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a very intriguing 
torture target, but...</i></font>

365
00:19:13,210 --> 00:19:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since that type has such a 
strong sense of purpose,</i></font>

366
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it tends to be hard to get them to talk.</i></font>

367
00:19:18,170 --> 00:19:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not only do they take a long time,</i></font>

368
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they'll criticize the system, 
spew their convictions,</i></font>

369
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and say a bunch of stuff 
no one asked about...</i></font>

370
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're a pain!</i></font>

371
00:19:25,930 --> 00:19:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What game will we play?</font>

372
00:19:28,030 --> 00:19:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we play in teams? 
I don't wanna do it alone!</font>

373
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's true.</font>

374
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about Reversi?</font>

375
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. You're too good at that one.</font>

376
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

377
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,200
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#c1c1c1"><font size="25">Sero & Mike</font></font></b></font>

378
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,200
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f0a647"><font size="25">Join the Fight!</font></font></b></font>

379
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,660
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#c1c1c1"><font size="25">Siu & Hugh</font></font></b></font>

380
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,660
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f0a647"><font size="25">Join the Fight!</font></font></b></font>

381
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, we'll play shogi-kuzushi!</font>

382
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm confident in my sense of balance!</font>

383
00:19:49,780 --> 00:19:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I've got this.</i></font>

384
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good, good.</font>

385
00:20:01,450 --> 00:20:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go, Mike-chan!</font>

386
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking good!</font>

387
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:07,470
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="25"><font color="#221923">TICKLE...</font></font></font></b></font>

388
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we win.</font>

389
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Grin...</i></font>

390
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:26,280
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="25"><b>

391
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hugh totally pulled the Old Maid.</i></font></b></font></font>

392
00:20:26,610 --> 00:20:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who falls for a simple bluff like that?</i></font>

393
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sero isn't going to pull 
the Old Maid from Hugh,</i></font>

394
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so that means we lose.</i></font>

395
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That pisses me off.</font>

396
00:20:45,930 --> 00:20:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My acting was pretty good, right?</font>

397
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought he'd be able to 
read Sero-san's hand,</font>

398
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I guess Siu-san can be tricked, too.</font>

399
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't play Old Maid very much.</font>

400
00:20:57,130 --> 00:20:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

401
00:20:58,370 --> 00:21:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no fun with only two people.</font>

402
00:21:00,570 --> 00:21:02,530
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="14"><font color="#030304">Young people 
don't often 
find a place
 in the world 
of torturers</font></font></b></font></font>

403
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:06,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the four of us should 
play it lots from now on!</font>

404
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

405
00:21:07,900 --> 00:21:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's play daifugo, too!</font>

406
00:21:09,610 --> 00:21:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we should.</font>

407
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was so much fun!</font>

408
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

409
00:21:16,450 --> 00:21:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice every once in a while.</font>

410
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it is.</font>

411
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we played so much, 
I can't remember the wins and losses.</font>

412
00:21:23,870 --> 00:21:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

413
00:21:25,730 --> 00:21:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, why don't we take 
the ideological offender?</font>

414
00:21:28,490 --> 00:21:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

415
00:21:29,370 --> 00:21:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's tough, but worthwhile, you know?</font>

416
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger that.</font>

417
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we won anyway. Right?</font>

418
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do this again sometime!</font>

419
00:21:40,970 --> 00:21:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time, we play as individuals.</font>

420
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll win.</font>

421
00:21:44,890 --> 00:21:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best, too!</font>

422
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, time to get to it. Let's go, Mike.</font>

423
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

424
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:54,790
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1a171c">A Later Day</font></b></font>

425
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Board games?</font>

426
00:21:57,390 --> 00:21:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course those don't 
count as a work expense.</font>

427
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, all right.</font>

428
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll let you play, too.</font>

429
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay?</font>

430
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the problem here!</font>

